I was living right there at Rājagaha in the Cool Wood at the Snake Tank Slope
I was living right there at Rājagaha in the River Tapodā Monastery
I was living right there near Rājagaha at the Squirrels Feeding Place in Bamboo Wood
At one time nanda I was living right there near Rājagaha at Jīvakas Mango Wood
